name: TST (Split NFT with Tolan Music)
description:
This artwork is animated from one of my favorite photographs. The original was taken from a rooftop in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong, one of the most visually stunning parts of the world I've had the pleasure of exploring!

This art is minted using my first split/colab contract on Tezos, Thanks to Matthew Plummer-Fernández & WG3.2! This contract splits the proceeds with me and the composer Tolan who created such a fun atmosphere for these vibrant buildings to live in! 

Twitter/IG: @patricklawler
Twitter: @tolan_music / IG: @tolanmusic
